1
00:00:43,250 --> 00:00:46,541
[LULU] Yes. Ginko committed
a grave crime, growl.

2
00:00:46,625 --> 00:00:49,500
Ginko is the reason
why Sumika is dead!

3
00:00:51,958 --> 00:00:56,791
How could you, Ginko?
I'll never forgive you bears!

4
00:00:56,875 --> 00:01:00,333
I'll ruin you, now. Every one!

5
00:01:02,333 --> 00:01:04,916
[gunshot]

6
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:08,333
[GINKO]
Growl!

7
00:01:10,041 --> 00:01:12,000
[KUREHA whimpers]

8
00:01:15,625 --> 00:01:19,666
[GINKO] From the beginning,
we hated you. But also,

9
00:01:19,750 --> 00:01:23,000
we loved you from the
beginning, as well.

10
00:01:23,083 --> 00:01:26,250
All we wanted was to become
true friends with you.

11
00:01:26,333 --> 00:01:31,125
So we had to cross the wall.

12
00:01:31,208 --> 00:01:36,125
[GINKO, LULU]
Yurikuma!

13
00:01:36,208 --> 00:01:38,500
Yurikuma Arashi!

14
00:03:11,125 --> 00:03:12,125
[STUDENTS chat]

15
00:03:12,208 --> 00:03:13,791
[CHOUKO]
Girls, this is, like, way bad!

16
00:03:13,875 --> 00:03:16,583
People are saying another
bear was here yesterday.

17
00:03:16,666 --> 00:03:19,583
[STUDENT A] Yeah, but I heard
it was exterminated immediately.

18
00:03:19,666 --> 00:03:21,416
[STUDENT B]
That same girl shot it, right?

19
00:03:21,500 --> 00:03:24,125
The one The Invisible Storm
isn't a huge fan of?

20
00:03:24,208 --> 00:03:27,333
Yeah, but, and don't tell anyone
cuz it's, like, way secret,

21
00:03:27,416 --> 00:03:30,875
apparently that bear is,
