00:04:46,333 --> 00:04:49,375
loved you, but you
pretended not to see.

31
00:04:49,458 --> 00:04:51,583
And then you tried
to abandon her.

32
00:04:51,666 --> 00:04:55,625
Now, you're paying the
price for that sin.

33
00:04:55,708 --> 00:04:57,375
Guess what, Reia?

34
00:04:57,458 --> 00:05:00,833
Your sweet girl, the precious
daughter you loved so much,

35
00:05:00,916 --> 00:05:02,875
is almost mine.

36
00:05:02,958 --> 00:05:05,291
And now I'll make her
my bride-in-the-box.

37
00:05:05,375 --> 00:05:07,208
Yes. Today.

38
00:05:07,291 --> 00:05:10,541
[BEAR SHOCK LADY]
Shock!

39
00:05:10,625 --> 00:05:12,041
Kuma shock!

40
00:05:12,125 --> 00:05:15,958
[YURIIKA] I'm going to eat
Kureha Tsubaki! Grrraow!

41
00:05:16,041 --> 00:05:17,375
[GINKO gasps]

42
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:23,500
[gasps]

43
00:05:25,083 --> 00:05:26,625
I lost it.

44
00:05:26,708 --> 00:05:29,000
[MITSUKO] You should be
thankful you're alive.

45
00:05:29,083 --> 00:05:30,833
For now, at least.

46
00:05:32,916 --> 00:05:35,125
Goodness, did I surprise you?

47
00:05:35,208 --> 00:05:38,916
Why are you here? I thought
you were dead. Growl, growl.

48
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:41,250
Well, you thought right,
because I am dead.

49
00:05:41,333 --> 00:05:44,666
It's crazy, but you're the only
one who can see me right now.

50
00:05:46,333 --> 00:05:49,375
Everything's fine.
Just think of me as a ghost

51
00:05:49,458 --> 00:05:52,791
named "Desire" that happens
to dwell inside you right here.

52
00:05:52,875 --> 00:05:53,833
[GINKO gasps]

53
00:05:53,916 --> 00:05:57,208
[laughs] Is that
explanation enough?

54
00:05:57,291 --> 00:05:58,291
[GINKO]
Where are we?

55
00:05:58,375 --> 00:06:00,500
[MITSUKO]
The Door to Friendship.

56
00:06:00,583 --> 00:06:02,750
The center of the
sky that divides

57
00:06:02,833 --> 00:06:04,916
the worlds of moon and forest.

58
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:09,000
This is the place where
true love is tested.

59
00:06:09,083 --> 00:06:10,833
Now, tell me
something, Ginko.

60
00:06:10,916 --> 00:06:12,083
I'm dying to hear

61
00:06:12,166 --> 00:06:15,083
