killed Sumika Izumino.

62
00:06:17,375 --> 00:06:20,250
[MITSUKO] I say early tomorrow
morning we come back here.

63
00:06:20,333 --> 00:06:22,291
Then, the flowerbed
can get fixed.

64
00:06:22,375 --> 00:06:24,791
I don't mind helping
you at all!

65
00:06:24,875 --> 00:06:27,416
Thanks, Mitsuko, that's
so generous of you!

66
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:30,291
Great. We're both in, are
you meeting us too, Kureha?

67
00:06:30,375 --> 00:06:32,041
Oh, yeah, uh-huh.

68
00:06:34,375 --> 00:06:35,250
[SUMIKA, KUREHA gasp]

69
00:06:35,333 --> 00:06:36,541
Who did that?

70
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:42,250
[MITSUKO] I sensed
something was wrong, then.

71
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:47,041
I had a rival at the
school who was also

72
00:06:47,125 --> 00:06:49,041
after my Kureha Tsubaki.

73
00:06:49,125 --> 00:06:53,250
A bear in human form other
than me. Well me and Konomi.

74
00:06:53,333 --> 00:06:55,083
If I didn't hurry
and make my move,

75
00:06:55,166 --> 00:06:58,833
another bear was going to get
to her before I could. So...

76
00:07:02,083 --> 00:07:04,125
Bye. I'm headed this way.

77
00:07:04,208 --> 00:07:05,958
See you in the morning.

78
00:07:08,083 --> 00:07:11,333
[MITSUKO] Listen, Sumika.
I have an idea about tomorrow.

79
00:07:11,416 --> 00:07:14,041
Why don't we arrange
a surprise for Kureha?

80
00:07:14,125 --> 00:07:15,500
[SUMIKA]
A surprise?

81
00:07:15,583 --> 00:07:17,875
I know someone with lilies
in bloom who would probably

82
00:07:17,958 --> 00:07:20,500
give us some. Don't you
think she'd love that?

83
00:07:20,583 --> 00:07:23,333
I can pick them up tonight so
we can plant them for her.

84
00:07:23,416 --> 00:07:24,458
Really?

85
00:07:24,541 --> 00:07:26,500
Yeah! It'll be great.

86
00:07:26,583 --> 00:07:29,458
So, tomorrow morning meet me
there early, and together we'll

87
00:07:29,541 --> 00:07:32,625
fill the flowerbed full of
lilies before she arrives!

88
00:07:32,708 --> 00:07:34,916
Okay, but what if she--

89
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:37,250
I bet it will make
Kureha so happy!

90
00:07:37,333 --> 00:07:40,500
It'll be just like a
magic fairy visited!

91
00:07:40,583 --> 00:07:41,541
[SUMIKA]
Uh.

92
00:07:44,750 --> 00:07:47,708
It's funny. That girl
would've done anything I said.

93
00:07:47,791 --> 00:07:51,333
All I had to do was
mention it was for Kureha.

94
00:07:51,416 --> 00:07:55,000
Now, come on, be honest
with me, won't you?

95
00:07:55,083 --> 00:07:56,416
--[crunch]
--[GINKO gasps]

96
00:07:59,916 --> 00:08:01,708
[MITSUKO]
The truth is, you found out

97
00:08:01,791 --> 00:08:05,000
that I was targeting
Sumika Izumino, didn't you?

98
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:12,916
[MITSUKO] You should learn
how to hide better.

99
