Following Sumika to see
what made her so great.

101
00:08:21,208 --> 00:08:23,583
Will you get some?
They are very lovely.

102
00:08:23,666 --> 00:08:27,541
[SUMIKA] What? Oh, you're one of
the new transfer students, hi.

103
00:08:30,458 --> 00:08:31,666
[GINKO]
Sniff, sniff.

104
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:33,583
--[SUMIKA laughs]
--[GINKO] Hm?

105
00:08:33,666 --> 00:08:35,375
They smell amazing.

106
00:08:35,458 --> 00:08:38,208
I'm guessing you must
be a fan of lilies, too.

107
00:08:38,291 --> 00:08:39,791
I adore them.

108
00:08:39,875 --> 00:08:42,916
They're lovely, and they make
me think of a special memory.

109
00:08:44,458 --> 00:08:48,083
A special memory with a friend,
a friend I happen to love.

110
00:08:50,458 --> 00:08:53,625
[SUMIKA] I won't back
down on that love.

111
00:08:53,708 --> 00:08:55,833
Because the love
my friend gave me

112
00:08:55,916 --> 00:08:58,250
can't be taken away by anyone.

113
00:09:00,291 --> 00:09:02,708
[SUMIKA gasps]
Oh! I'm sorry!

114
00:09:02,791 --> 00:09:05,041
I bet it was weird for me
to say something like that

115
00:09:05,125 --> 00:09:07,041
when we've only just met.

116
00:09:07,125 --> 00:09:10,583
[MITSUKO] Yeah. You were
jealous of her, weren't you?

117
00:09:10,666 --> 00:09:14,250
The love you dreamed about,
and wanted so badly from Kureha,

118
00:09:14,333 --> 00:09:17,458
had already been
given to another girl.

119
00:09:19,833 --> 00:09:21,625
[LULU]
Growl.

120
00:09:22,916 --> 00:09:26,500
[MITSUKO] And yet, you still
wanted to see her again.

121
00:09:26,583 --> 00:09:29,250
In fact, this time you didn't
even tell your partner

122
00:09:29,333 --> 00:09:31,416
what you were up to.

123
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:34,625
Why go? Did you plan
to warn her about me?

124
00:09:34,708 --> 00:09:37,500
[GINKO]
Yes. That was the idea.

125
00:09:40,625 --> 00:09:44,541
Oh, stupid me. How could I go
and lose the hairpin again?

126
00:09:44,625 --> 00:09:45,666
[GINKO]
Here.

127
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:46,541
[SUMIKA]
Uh!

128
00:09:49,916 --> 00:09:53,166
[SUMIKA]
Ginko! You found it! Thank you!

129
00:09:53,250 --> 00:09:55,708
What a relief!
I'm so silly.

130
00:09:55,791 --> 00:09:58,708
This is the second time
someone's found this pin for me.

131
00:09:58,791 --> 00:10:01,625
I lost it the day of the
entrance ceremony, too.

132
00:10:01,708 --> 00:10:03,666
The friend I told you
about yesterday?

133
00:10:03,750 --> 00:10:06,625
She's the one who who found
it before. Neat, huh?

134
00:10:06,708 --> 00:10:09,416
She found it
for you before?

135
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:13,208
Yep. This hairpin has brought
me friendship and love.

136
00:10:13,291 --> 00:10:16,083
I like to think of it
as my special charm.

137
00:10:16,166 --> 00:10:18,625
Thank you,
it means so much to me.

138
00:10:18,708 --> 00:10:21,375
I really, really
appreciate it, Ginko!

139
00:10:21,458 --> 00:10:24,541
Now, I'd better hurry up
and run, or I'll be late!

140
00:10:24,625 --> 00:10:26,208
[GINKO gasps]
Wai--

141
00:10:30,916 --> 00:10:36,791
[GINKO] I was first, though. She
found me first. Growl, growl.

142
00:10:37,750 --> 00:10:39,125
[MITSUKO]
That's right.

143
00:10:39,208 --> 00:10:41,125
If you had gone ahead
and stopped her then,

144
00:10:41,208 --> 00:10:45,083
Sumika Izumino wouldn't have
had to die. Kureha Tsubaki

145
00:10:45,166 --> 00:10:48,708
wouldn't have had to lose
her very best friend, either.

146
00:10:48,791 --> 00:10:54,666
[GINKO] I know. I couldn't
help it. Sumika was in my way.

147
00:10:54,750 --> 00:10:59,208
[MITSUKO laughs] And we
exclude those in our way.

148
00:10:59,291 --> 00:11:01,416
It would be so much easier
if we were just honest

149
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:03,750
about what we want.

150
00:11:03,833 --> 00:11:10,458
[GINKO] So that's the truth. I'm
guilty. I wanted Sumika to die.

151
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,458
[MITSUKO]
Well, good morning, Sumika!

152
00:11:14,541 --> 00:11:16,375
[SUMIKA gasps]

153
00:11:16,458 --> 00:11:19,583
[FEMALE VOICE]
Shock!

154
00:11:19,666 --> 00:11:21,166
Kuma shock!

155
00:11:21,250 --> 00:11:24,416
[MITSUKO] Such a lovely morning.
And I'm practically starving!

156
00:11:24,500 --> 00:11:25,708
Growl-growl
Chomp-chomp...

157
00:11:25,791 --> 00:11:28,708
You witnessed me attacking
sweet little Sumika,

158
00:11:28,791 --> 00:11:33,375
and you just sat there and
watched. You allowed her die.

159
00:11:33,458 --> 00:11:37,083
You could've saved her,
but you didn't.

160
00:11:37,166 --> 00:11:39,791
Technically, yes,
I'm the one who ate her.

161
00:11:39,875 --> 00:11:43,750
But who was the one
that really killed her?

162
00:11:43,833 --> 00:11:44,875
It was me.

163
00:11:44,958 --> 00:11:46,291
[MITSUKO]
Indeed it was!

164
00:11:46,375 --> 00:11:49,541
In that moment,
you were a slave of desire.

165
00:11:49,625 --> 00:11:52,958
Jealousy got ahold of you and
drove you to a terrible crime.

166
00:11:53,041 --> 00:11:55,541
[GINKO] I'm a criminal bear.
Growl, growl.

167
00:11:55,625 --> 00:11:58,666
[MITSUKO] Yes. However,
is there really any creature

168
00:11:58,750 --> 00:12:01,625
that doesn't sin
in order to live?

169
00:12:01,708 --> 00:12:04,875
Kureha Tsubaki forgot you,
her friend,

170
00:12:04,958 --> 00:12:08,166
and then she gave her
love to Sumika instead.

171
00:12:08,250 --> 00:12:12,125
Now, pay attention. Only one
thing in this world is certain,

172
00:12:12,208 --> 00:12:14,833
and, believe you me,
it's not friendship or love.

173
00:12:14,916 --> 00:12:16,708
[GINKO gasps]

174
00:12:16,791 --> 00:12:20,375
Desire is the only thing
you can count on, dear Ginko.

175
00:12:20,458 --> 00:12:25,625
Love is a savage emotion.
To love another is to rule them.

176
00:12:25,708 --> 00:12:27,250
To want to become one with them

177
00:12:27,333 --> 00:12:30,291
so badly you consume
them is truly cruel.

178
00:12:30,375 --> 00:12:34,041
I know something else you might
want to hear. Shall I tell you?

179
00:12:34,125 --> 00:12:37,666
There's another bear at
that school besides us.

180
00:12:37,750 --> 00:12:39,750
A very cunning bear, at that.

181
00:12:39,833 --> 00:12:41,916
She got Kureha to kill me,

182
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:45,708
and she got Lulu Yurigasaki
to betray you.

183
00:12:45,791 --> 00:12:48,458
I hate to admit it, but that
bitch-bear had all of us

184
00:12:48,541 --> 00:12:50,458
dancing to her
own little tune.

185
00:12:50,541 --> 00:12:52,041
[YURIIKA]
Chomp, chomp, grrraow...

186
00:12:52,125 --> 00:12:55,583
[MITSUKO] Everything she's done
is because she's after Kureha.

187
00:12:55,666 --> 00:12:57,916
If you don't hurry and stop her,

188
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:01,208
you'll lose Kureha
forever this time.

189
00:13:05,083 --> 00:13:08,250
Are you ready to become
one with me, Ginko?

190
00:13:08,333 --> 00:13:11,625
