to prove your love!

191
00:13:23,541 --> 00:13:25,500
[MITSUKO]
Graow, graow, graow, graow!

192
00:13:25,583 --> 00:13:27,958
Growl, ha, ha, ha, ha!

193
00:13:30,583 --> 00:13:33,500
[FEMALE VOICE]
♪ Kuma ga aku. ♪

194
00:13:38,125 --> 00:13:42,750
[GINKO] I'm going to eat her.
I have to. Growl, growl.

195
00:13:49,125 --> 00:13:53,333
[sirens blaring]

196
00:13:58,541 --> 00:14:00,916
[CHOUKO] These photos were
totally discovered in the locker

197
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:03,000
of Kaoru Harishima,
who recently, like,

198
00:14:03,083 --> 00:14:05,458
way died in a bear attack.

199
00:14:07,458 --> 00:14:09,958
Konomi Yurikawa,
as you can see,

200
00:14:10,041 --> 00:14:13,166
was actually a bear
disguised as a human girl.

201
00:14:16,791 --> 00:14:18,916
This is scary, like way.

202
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:21,500
Bears got across the wall
pretending to be human,

203
00:14:21,583 --> 00:14:25,500
and they've like way eaten our
friends one after the other!

204
00:14:25,583 --> 00:14:27,500
[STUDENTS murmur]

205
00:14:27,583 --> 00:14:32,000
[CHOUKO] We all see what this,
like, means, don't we?

206
00:14:32,083 --> 00:14:34,416
That's right, there's,
like, a bear in this class.

207
00:14:34,500 --> 00:14:37,208
A bear hiding among us,
like, for real!

208
00:14:39,041 --> 00:14:41,250
[CHOUKO] Bears, like, way
stick out from our crowd.

209
00:14:41,333 --> 00:14:43,875
Bears refuse to
like fit in with us.

210
00:14:43,958 --> 00:14:47,375
Bears are evil and can't
follow social cues!

211
00:14:48,958 --> 00:14:51,875
[LIFE COOL] Here we go.
They've started up again.

212
00:14:51,958 --> 00:14:54,291
[LIFE BEAUTY]
Yep, but, Kureha Tsubaki

213
00:14:54,375 --> 00:14:56,375
is attending the
meeting this time!

214
00:14:56,458 --> 00:14:58,750
[LIFE COOL] They made her
a friend at this late date?

215
00:14:58,833 --> 00:15:02,750
Very interesting. Have they
canceled her exclusion, then?

216
00:15:02,833 --> 00:15:05,458
[LIFE SEXY]
Oh, who can tell?

217
00:15:05,541 --> 00:15:09,333
Those girls are always looking
for some "evil" to exclude.

218
00:15:09,416 --> 00:15:10,958
It doesn't matter to
them whether the evil

219
00:15:11,041 --> 00:15:14,666
is a person or a bear
or even really evil.

220
00:15:14,750 --> 00:15:17,416
