224
00:15:27,250 --> 00:15:29,458
Shaba-da-doo.

225
00:15:29,541 --> 00:15:31,541
[beep]

226
00:15:31,625 --> 00:15:33,875
[LIFE COOL]
Shall I put in another coin?

227
00:15:33,958 --> 00:15:38,208
[LIFE SEXY]
Yeah. Shaba-da... doo?

228
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:43,166
[CHOUKO] Let us now begin
the Exclusion Ceremony.

229
