00:16:31,625 --> 00:16:32,833
[KUREHA whimpers]

234
00:16:32,916 --> 00:16:36,166
[KUREHA]
Tell me, Mom. Did I...?

235
00:16:36,250 --> 00:16:38,541
Did I do the right
thing that day?

236
00:16:41,958 --> 00:16:43,458
[KUREHA]
Lulu.

237
00:16:43,541 --> 00:16:46,041
[LULU]
Kure-pie. Lulu knows the truth.

238
00:16:46,125 --> 00:16:48,166
She found out what
Ginko did to Sumika.

239
00:16:48,250 --> 00:16:49,416
[gasps]

240
00:16:49,500 --> 00:16:52,750
Yes. Ginko committed a
very grave crime, growl.

241
00:16:52,833 --> 00:16:56,708
Ginko is why Sumika's dead.
She helped the killer!

242
00:16:56,791 --> 00:17:00,125
[gasps] Ginko, is that true?

243
00:17:00,208 --> 00:17:02,833
[GINKO]
Yes, it's true. Growl, growl.

244
00:17:02,916 --> 00:17:07,375
I killed Sumika Izumino.
It was me.

245
00:17:07,458 --> 00:17:08,416
[KUREHA gasps]

246
00:17:09,083 --> 00:17:13,000
[music box plays]

247
00:17:15,416 --> 00:17:18,125
[KUREHA]
Mitsuko Yurizono killed Sumika.

248
00:17:18,208 --> 00:17:24,875
I know that for a fact, so,
why would Ginko confess to it?

249
00:17:24,958 --> 00:17:27,333
What's the truth,
and what's a lie?

250
00:17:27,416 --> 00:17:30,500
I don't understand any of this.

251
00:17:39,041 --> 00:17:40,333
Yes?

252
00:17:40,416 --> 00:17:42,833
[MODIFIED VOICE]
Is your love the real thing?

253
00:17:42,916 --> 00:17:46,291
This call is a challenge
from the Wall of Severance.

254
00:17:46,375 --> 00:17:48,166
Kureha Tsubaki...

255
00:17:48,250 --> 00:17:49,958
[MODIFIED VOICE]
...if your love is true,

256
00:17:50,041 --> 00:17:52,625
go to the lily bed immediately.

257
00:17:52,708 --> 00:17:54,916
The bear in question
will be waiting for you.

258
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:57,416
[KUREHA gasps]
She's at the flowerbed?

259
00:17:57,500 --> 00:17:58,916
Ginko's waiting for me?

260
00:17:59,000 --> 00:18:01,166
[YURIIKA]
Give yourself over to the bears,

261
00:18:01,250 --> 00:18:04,208
and your love will be approved.

262
00:18:04,291 --> 00:18:06,416
[KUREHA]
I'm going to go talk to Ginko.

263
00:18:06,500 --> 00:18:10,166
And this time, I'm going to
find out what really happened.

264
00:18:10,250 --> 00:18:12,875
[LIFE COOL] Huh. To think
she masqueraded as us

265
00:18:12,958 --> 00:18:15,833
to make a prank call
to Kureha Tsubaki.

266
00:18:15,916 --> 00:18:19,500
Oh, that Yuriika Hakonaka.
She is guilty.

267
00:18:19,583 --> 00:18:22,041
[LIFE BEAUTY] Mm-hm. Although,
what she's about to do

268
00:18:22,125 --> 00:18:24,666
is why she made the contract
with us to begin with.

269
00:18:24,750 --> 00:18:29,375
So, she's probably ready for the
consequences. Sparkle, sparkle!

270
00:18:29,458 --> 00:18:32,750
[LIFE SEXY] All shall be as
according to Kumaria's will.

271
00:18:32,833 --> 00:18:37,125
For that is sexy. Shaba-da-doo.

272
00:18:38,250 --> 00:18:39,833
[KUREHA panting]

273
00:18:39,916 --> 00:18:43,166
[KUREHA] Ginko, what
happened between us?

274
00:18:43,250 --> 00:18:45,916
I want to know the truth.

275
00:18:49,125 --> 00:18:54,708
[YURIIKA] Dearest Reia, do you
remember that stormy night?

276
00:18:54,791 --> 00:18:57,125
Do you remember the
moment I ate you?

277
00:18:57,208 --> 00:18:59,708
Do you remember when I put
you in the box of myself

278
00:18:59,791 --> 00:19:01,291
to fill in my gaps.

279
00:19:01,375 --> 00:19:06,166
But I wasn't fulfilled,
I was still so empty.

280
00:19:06,250 --> 00:19:09,375
[YURIIKA laughs]
I figured out why, though.

281
00:19:09,458 --> 00:19:12,375
It was because you had given
all your love away to her.

282
00:19:12,458 --> 00:19:16,250
So I decided to
wait, until now.

283
00:19:16,333 --> 00:19:18,958
I waited until that girl who
stole your love from me

284
00:19:19,041 --> 00:19:22,208
finally grew up.
And I waited as your love,

285
00:19:22,291 --> 00:19:26,000
gradually and beautifully,
blossomed inside of her.

286
00:19:26,083 --> 00:19:29,416
I did all this in a blank
world robbed of color.

287
00:19:29,500 --> 00:19:33,208
I waited, and
waited, and waited.

288
00:19:33,291 --> 00:19:38,000
At last, yes.

289
00:19:38,083 --> 00:19:40,250
The flower has bloomed.

290
00:19:40,333 --> 00:19:43,291
Today, I will eat your daughter.

291
00:19:43,375 --> 00:19:48,458
Today, I will eat
Kureha Tsubaki. Grraow!

292
00:19:48,541 --> 00:19:54,125
[KUREHA panting]
Ginko! Where are you?

293
00:19:54,208 --> 00:19:59,583
[YURIIKA] Pant, pant, grrraow.
Pant, pant, grrraow.

294
00:19:59,666 --> 00:20:00,708
[KUREHA gasps]

295
00:20:00,791 --> 00:20:03,291
[YURIIKA]
Grrraowrrrr.

296
00:20:03,375 --> 00:20:08,333
[KUREHA] Uh! This... This is
wrong. That bear isn't Ginko.

297
00:20:08,416 --> 00:20:12,000
[YURIIKA] Oh, Reia.
She looks just like you.

298
00:20:12,083 --> 00:20:17,000
Her eyes, her hair.
She even has your smell.

299
00:20:17,083 --> 00:20:22,250
Kureha Tsubaki!
Give your love to me! Grrraow!

300
00:20:22,333 --> 00:20:25,416
You and I are going
to become one forever!

301
00:20:34,583 --> 00:20:37,875
Take my kiss, now,
Kureha, my darling.

302
00:20:37,958 --> 00:20:39,416
This kiss is a special one.

303
00:20:39,500 --> 00:20:42,208
It's for my precious
bride-in-the-box.

304
00:20:45,291 --> 00:20:48,125
[YURIIKA]
Grr-rrao-rraow!

305
00:20:48,208 --> 00:20:49,291
[gasps]

306
00:20:49,375 --> 00:20:51,708
That was, like, a way,
super close call.

307
00:20:51,791 --> 00:20:53,958
[KUREHA]
Chouko? Oh.

308
00:20:54,041 --> 00:20:56,125
[CHOUKO]
The bear ran away! After it!

309
00:20:56,208 --> 00:20:58,500
[footsteps]

310
00:20:58,583 --> 00:21:00,208
[KUREHA]
Wait, that's...!

311
00:21:01,583 --> 00:21:06,000
[YURIIKA crying]

312
00:21:06,083 --> 00:21:11,208
[REIA]
Yuriika. Yuriika. Yuriika.

313
00:21:11,291 --> 00:21:14,166
Yuriika? Yuriika!

314
00:21:14,250 --> 00:21:19,916
[YURIIKA sighs]
Reia, you found me again.

315
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:23,541
I missed you so much. Oh,
how I've longed to see you

316
00:21:23,625 --> 00:21:26,916
just one more time, and here you
are. It's all I've dreamed about

317
00:21:27,000 --> 00:21:30,041
since that awful
night I ate you.

318
00:21:30,125 --> 00:21:33,125
Oh, Reia. I've been holding
on to something precious

319
00:21:33,208 --> 00:21:35,125
I need to return to you.

320
00:21:35,208 --> 00:21:37,791
In a box, in the middle
of my drawers,

321
00:21:37,875 --> 00:21:40,125
"The Moon Girl and
the Forest Girl",

322
00:21:40,208 --> 00:21:44,875
that box has the rest of
your picture book in it.

323
00:21:44,958 --> 00:21:49,458
It was the dream of our
love that never materialized.

324
00:21:51,333 --> 00:21:53,000
I couldn't seem
to help myself.

325
00:21:53,083 --> 00:21:58,166
I wanted it so desperately
I stole it. Please forgive me.

326
00:22:05,583 --> 00:22:07,625
[YURIIKA]
Yes, you're right.

327
00:22:07,708 --> 00:22:12,458
That will be their destiny.
Their rightful future.

328
00:22:12,541 --> 00:22:16,291
You know the truth, don't you,
Reia? You know how I feel.

329
00:22:16,375 --> 00:22:21,583
I think you knew before
I did. And I still do.

330
00:22:21,666 --> 00:22:25,416
[YURIIKA] And we'll be
friends forever, won't we?

331
00:22:25,500 --> 00:22:30,333
[REIA]
Yes. Forever and ever.

332
00:22:30,416 --> 00:22:32,125
[YURIIKA]
I love you.

333
00:24:17,083 --> 00:24:19,416
[KUREHA] I can't believe
Miss Yuriika was the bear

334
00:24:19,500 --> 00:24:21,250
that killed Mom.

335
00:24:21,791 --> 00:24:26,708
[YURIIKA] That will be their
destiny. Their rightful future.

336
00:24:26,791 --> 00:24:30,958
Here it is. The end.
Ginko's and my future?

337
00:24:31,041 --> 00:24:33,916
It can't be. That's impossible!

